name: Russians on Vacation
description:
Tulum Archaeological Zone
Tulum, 2019

This is a beach that is part of a archaeological site tour in Tulum. It’s basically a museum with its own private beach. 

The three fellas in the water showed up first thing and actually ran through the site to get to the beach first. 

Around the other side of the rocky outcropping is a second beach closed off to everyone except the sea turtles that show up every year to lay eggs at the site.
